description: Development of 55-91 Knightsbridge (including retention of Knightsbridge and Wilton Place facades) to provide retail (Class A1) at basement and ground floor levels, office (Class B1) at part ground, part first and part second floor levels and 21 residential flats at part first, part second and third to fifth floor levels. Off street servicing and new sub basement car park.  Removal of replacement of existing street tree on William Street.  Restoration and repair of external facades and roofs to 3-7 William Street (consecutive) including reinstatement of original roof profile at 4 William Street, conversion of first to third floor levels of 3 and 4 William Street for residential purposes (Class C3). (Proposal 1- Demolition of 1-2 William Street and rebuilding the facades in facsimile with internal linkages to 55-91 Knightsbridge: Proposal 2- Demolition of 1-2 William Street and replacement with a redesigned building with internal linkages to 55-91 Knightsbridge).
